description:
Newborn Baby Care, Advice, lessons, Tips & Tricks.

This app contains the following lessons to newborn parents:

"1" = "Congratulations!";
"2" = "Caring Begins at Birth";
"3" = "Your Newborn\’s Hospital Check-up";
"4" = "Ten Fingers and Ten Toes";
"5" = "Special Care for Your Newborn";
"6" = "When Your Newborn Cries";
"7" = "Changing Your Newborn’s Diaper";
"8" = "Brest or bottle feeding";
"9" = "Feeding Your Newborn";
"10" = "Bathing Your Newborn";
"11" = "Dressing Your Newborn";
"12" = "Shhh!! We’re Sleeping";
"13" = "Keeping Your Baby Safe";
"14" = "Your Newborn’s Admirers";
"15" = "Taking Your Newborn Out";
"16" = "If Your Newborn Gets a Cold";
"17" = "If You Have Questions";
"18" = "Well-baby Check-ups";
"19" = "When to Call Your Pediatrician";
